(1454, 3, '2011-11-10 12:50:52', '2011-11-10 11:50:52', '<h1>friskis&amp;svettis lidingö in brief</h1>\n<strong>Welcome to Friskis&amp;Svettis Lidingö!</strong>\nBy becoming a member of Friskis&amp;Svettis Lidingö, you gain access to our  fitness centre in Lidingö. We offer a wide range of all-round training and more specific forms of exercise.\n\n<strong>Our organisation\n</strong>Friskis&amp;Svettis is a non-profit organisation, and is entirely financed by our members. The organisation was founded in 1978, F&amp;S Lidingö in 1982. The association has approximately 5500 members and 140 members are involved as “Jympa” instructors, Spinning instructors, Gym instructors and hosts.\n\n<strong>Our idea\n</strong>To offer fun and easily accessible high quality exercise suited to fit the general public.\n\n<strong>Our mission\n</strong>To get as many people as possible to exercise and experience the joy of movement/exercise.\n\n<strong>Our vision\n</strong>A Lidingö where people feel good, enjoy working out and are given that extra zest for life that exercising provides.\n\nFor more information please visit our fitness centre  or call 08-767 59 53.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Friskis&Svettis in Brief', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '218-revision', '', '', '2011-11-10 12:50:52', '2011-11-10 11:50:52', '', 218, 'http://friskis.stropdev.se/218-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
